O '''indekso le manushutne baryaripenasko''' si labyardo tar e [[Phandle Nasiye]], ginindoy o [[choripen]], [[lekhavipenesko janglipen]], [[jivipenasko shaypen]] tay aver zorale butya [[them]]endar. O kamipen si te ginel o [[jivipenasko mishtipen]]. But manusha labyaren les te te janen kana yek them si andar i yekto, duyto vay trito lumya.

O indekso kerdilo [[1990]] bersheste, tar o [[pakistan]]o [[Mahbub ul Haq]] tay sas labyardo tar o [[Baryaripenasko Programo le Phandle Nasiyengo]] (katar [[1993]]) ando bershutno [[Reporto le Manushtne Baryaripenasko]].

Kana kerel pes o indekso, le may zorale butya so si ginyarde si:
* yek lungo tay sasto jivipen, palal o jivipenasko shaypen
* o lekhavipenesko janglipen tay o Sikikheryako phiripen
* dosta love te jivel mishto, palal o [[andrutno bruto produkto]] (ABP) kay [[komparativi kidipenaski zor]] (KKZ).

